snippet.title: Johnny Depp trial: Amber Heard says case has been “incredibly painful” as it nears end | 5 News
snippet.description:
► Subscribe to 5 News: http://bit.ly/5NewsSub 

► After three weeks of extraordinary evidence, today was the final day of Johnny Depp's libel case against the Sun. The actor is suing the paper for calling him a "wife beater", which he denies. In the last hour, his ex-wife Amber Heard spoke outside the High Court, saying the case had been an "incredibly painful" experience. 

► Amber Heard: Johnny Depp threw glass bottles at me “like grenades”
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N1mpBn6u5-k&t=1s

► #5News #News #JohnnyDepp
